{"tid":457262,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"女朋友好唔注重衛生","createTime":"2017-11-03T16:22:37.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-04T04:06:47.000Z","uid":107566,"like":5,"dislike":26,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"a9f0f216b67120499b710de2825247c4cb7ffd00","tid":457262,"uid":107566,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-03T16:22:37.000Z","msg":"成日都唔沖涼 可能幾日先沖一次<br />\n有時做完運動 出完汗都可以唔沖涼 就咁等佢乾就上床訓教<br />\n腳毛又唔剃 勁長勁明顯 <br />\n同佢講過又唔理我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n個人又好無sense 佢個世界好天真 <br />\n但佢好愛我 好專一<br />\n個樣都幾好<br />\n我都對佢好有感情但我唔知點樣對住佢過人世<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9ba2eae1106dc7f177681a137fbee11239ae3dec","tid":457262,"uid":73909,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-03T16:23:43.000Z","msg":"分手啦"},{"pid":"9f7f9a92d98c3498a9e957b0805fa2817f107f48","tid":457262,"uid":2419,"like":22,"dislike":3,"score":19,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-03T16:25:10.000Z","msg":"你幫佢奶汗囉on9仔<br />\n老泥就撈飯<br />\n閪屎就搽麵包<br />\n腳毛長就剃好拎去煲湯飲左佢<br />\n唔撚洗我教呀？"},{"pid":"b781a056e049db2a526b14571e18b41dba61c54f","tid":457262,"uid":107566,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-03T16:25:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>分手啦</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"646befa7d053447a2737722e2496c8bb3f673c0d","tid":457262,"uid":7954,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-03T16:25:38.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"e42bc669fbde25ca64c7327e6cfdc61767965d91","tid":457262,"uid":107566,"like":12,"dislike":2,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-03T16:35:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你幫佢奶汗囉on9仔<br />\n老泥就撈飯<br />\n閪屎就搽麵包<br />\n腳毛長就剃好拎去煲湯飲左佢<br />\n唔撚洗我教呀？</blockquote><br />\n唔怪得咁多人block你"},{"pid":"4d266fc98d41f21b0c4339526136b59f6c756f63","tid":457262,